  "description": "Relatively small, but bright and attractive, this refrigerator has a retro design that can become the centerpiece of your kitchen design. The model is two-chamber and two-door with a total useful volume of 212 liters. The freezer is located on top, its volume is small 46 liters, the freezing capacity is only 2 kg / day, but at the same time, the minimum maintained temperature inside the freezer is -32 °C. As for the refrigeration compartment, its useful volume is at the level of 166 liters. The manufacturer provides support for the automatic defrost function, but there is no talk of No Frost technology. Another important advantage of the Gunter&Hauer FN 240 R refrigerator is its economical power consumption. Thus, the model has been assigned the energy class A ++, the energy consumption claimed by the manufacturer per year is 173 kWh.",
